name: "Art Establishment" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing made on my phone...out of frustration...] I'm a fan of ARTZ for ARTZ sake. I like to make. I don't mind making a couple of bux, but I'm not changing my "style" (or LACK-OF-STYLE) for anyone. (Not sorry.) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
